data.description: Move right in to 604 Sunny Brook Road. Conveniently located in Country Meadows you'll have quick accessibility to recreation, shopping, dining and the interstate. This 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath brick and vinyl sided home is sure to impress. From the 2 story foyer you have an office with lovely French doors and the formal dining room. Continue in to the main living space which features a gorgeous gas fireplace and wet bar. Enjoy your view from the breakfast nook, that includes a window seat with storage below. The open kitchen overlooks the fully-fenced back yard featuring a deck, pergola, and established trees. Also on the main level is a half bath, laundry room, attached 3 car garage and an amazing sunroom with access to the back yard. Head upstairs to find the primary suite with separate jetted bath and shower, walk-in closet and an adorable reading nook perched above the front door. The four additional bedrooms share a full bath with dual sinks and a laundry chute to the laundry below. Don't forget about the basement which offers almost 1000 sq ft of finished area including a wet bar and a full bathroom. The unfinished portion is a blank canvas, with storage shelves installed. Inspection from June of 2023 available.
